32
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,280
What are we doing?

33
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:44,159
Can't you see?

34
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,159
His Majesty has issued a decree.

35
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,479
You'll soon be my woman.

36
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,479
How could you be so shameless?

37
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,560
Regent,

38
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,680
