39
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:55,120
what you promised me.

40
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:57,400
Submit to me obediently.

41
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,719
I'll let you keep this male consort.

42
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,759
Cheng Ziru,

43
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,840
you're a scholar after all.

44
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,952
Have you no shame at all?

45
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:07,199
Since I'm a male consort,

46
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,919
