47
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,400
Moreover,

48
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,280
romantic company and fair ladies

49
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,199
have always been refined pursuits.

50
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:20,039
Besides, Her Majesty hasn't

51
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,080
married you yet.

52
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,280
Even if I marry him,

53
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,360
you'll still belong to me.

54
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:30,879
He formally granted you to me.

55
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,664
Don't even think of escaping.

56
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:41,439
Yes, Your Majesty.

57
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,199
Just you wait.

58
