=Episode 19=

59
00:04:07,648 --> 00:04:08,560
(Xuanming Palace)

60
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,680
The border wars remain stalemated.

61
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,400
Since Your Majesty decreed the marriage
between the Regent

62
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,680
and the Empress Dowager,

63
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,639
it's best to hold the ceremony swiftly

64
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,879
to bless the realm,

65
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:20,879
ensuring our dynasty's eternal peace.

66
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:23,319
Well said.

67
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,680
How could I neglect such importance?

68
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,720
Your Majesty,

69
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:31,480
regarding yesterday's
divine consultation,

70
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:35,240
should we inform the ministers?

71
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,800
What divine consultation?

72
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,319
About your wedding
to the Empress Dowager.

73
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,120
Ministers,

74
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,399
to dispel the ominous celestial signs,

75
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,959
I visited Astrological Bureau
with the Empress Dowager

76
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,000
to consult the oracle.

77
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:48,399
Unexpectedly,

78
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,720
all auspicious dates

79
00:04:49,728 --> 00:04:51,920
showed Yin hexagram omens.

80
00:04:52,672 --> 00:04:55,800
The Yin hexagram indicates misfortune.

81
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,279
It's ill-omened.

82
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:59,680
I asked Heaven for guidance.

83
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,480
Yet this time,

84
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,759
a Yang response emerged.

85
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,519
Heaven told me

86
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,720
unclear circumstances exist,

87
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,600
thus requiring postponement.

88
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,639
Ominous signs remained.

89
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,360
I couldn't just stop.

90
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,639
Thinking it over,

91
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,879
I consulted again,

92
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,600
asking whether border conflicts
had caused the delay

93
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,000
of the wedding.

94
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,240
This time,

95
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:21,279
heaven finally gave clear instructions

96
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:22,879
with a Yin-Yang sign.

97
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,319
I could finally breathe easier.

98
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:29,120
I intended to avert national calamity.

99
00:05:29,248 --> 00:05:30,360
Yet unexpectedly,

100
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:32,120
Heaven has its design.

101
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:34,319
It seems the wedding

102
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:37,920
can only wait till the border wars cease

103
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,959
and then be decided.

104
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:40,759
Regent,

105
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:44,560
we must prioritize the greater good.

106
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,839
Since Heaven decrees it so,

107
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,480
I raise no objection.

108
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,720
Regarding the borders,

109
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,480
I believe the prolonged stalemate

110
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,480
stems from lacking capable personnel.

111
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,839
Though Marquis Jingyuan achieved merits,

112
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,000
he's advanced in years

113
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,160
without competent strategists.

114
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,759
I recommend someone

115
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,480
whose strategies
rival legendary advisors'.

116
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,040
If he assists Marquis Jingyuan,

117
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,800
the border wars will surely end swiftly,

118
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:28,560
resolving our crisis
and Your Majesty's worries.

119
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,759
Whom do you recommend?

120
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,120
Tell me promptly.

121
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,360
The very person is

122
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,680
Your Majesty
and the First Prince's tutor,

123
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,199
Cheng Ziru.

124
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,860
Regent,

125
00:06:46,848 --> 00:06:48,800
are you trying to send him to his death?

126
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,480
Your Majesty is mistaken.

127
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,759
In peril, duty calls every man.

128
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:55,720
Shouldn't a true man serve his country

129
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,720
and sovereign?

130
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,680
A true man dies for his nation.

131
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,040
Are the soldiers at the border
allowed to die,

132
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:04,120
but Cheng Ziru cannot die?

133
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:06,839
Your Majesty,

134
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,680
I'll go to the frontier

135
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,360
to assist Marquis Jingyuan.

136
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:15,199
Grant me this chance to prove my worth.

137
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,120
Cheng Ziru,

138
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,360
you're a civil official.

139
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,800
Your Majesty, issue an edict

140
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,600
permitting me to go to the border

141
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,399
to fulfill my devotion

142
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,040
to the country and Your Majesty.

143
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:31,839
Well said.

144
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,720
You're worthy of being my tutor.

145
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,600
I shall personally see you off.

146
00:07:48,909 --> 00:07:52,928
(Yixiang Palace)

147
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,352
Your Majesty.

148
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,759
Yu Feng,

149
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,199
I...

150
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:27,120
I need to ask a favor of you.

151
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,279
As Ziru journeys to the border,

152
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:34,080
I want you to protect him in secret.

153
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,279
I refuse.

154
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,000
Fine.

155
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:43,679
But

156
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,240
if you want me to go,

157
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,080
I'll go.

158
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,679
I never imagined

159
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:09,159
