160
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,279
Yes.

161
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,919
I love him.

162
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,600
- Then I...
- Yu Feng.

163
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:24,960
Whether in the past, present,

164
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,039
or future,

165
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,000
